title: PML-N’s Armaghan Subhani wins NA-70 seat
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Chaudhry Armaghan Subhani of the Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz (PML-N) has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-70 Sialkot-I by securing 123,437 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was independent candidate Hafiz Hamid Raza who bagged 112,117 votes.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 52.6 per cent in the constituency.
